Class KinesisVideoStreamStartSelector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.services.rekognition.model.KinesisVideoStreamStartSelector

    public class KinesisVideoStreamStartSelector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

    Specifies the starting point in a Kinesis stream to start processing. You can use the producer timestamp or the fragment number. For more information, see Fragment.
